import React from 'react'

const Edit = (props) => {
    return (
        <>
            <Modal
                {...props}
                size="md"
                aria-labelledby="contained-modal-title-vcenter"
                centered
            >
                <Modal.Header>
                    <Modal.Title id="contained-modal-title-vcenter">
                        Edit User
                    </Modal.Title>
                </Modal.Header>
                <Modal.Body>
                    <EditForm uid={ID} type={type} />
                </Modal.Body>
                <Modal.Footer>
                    <Button onClick={props.onHide}>Close</Button>
                </Modal.Footer>
            </Modal>
        </>
    )
}

export default Edit
